<p>I recall anti nuclear badges, “mutate now, avoid the rush!”.</p> 
<p>Energy exploitation has spawned an unprecedented hubris and arrogance of thought. Transportation has disintegrated and fragmented society. Communication has dissociated human beings yet further into a virtual ego in which manipulation and distraction fuel economic growth – also known as DEBT.</p> 
<p>Now I agree that there are benefits that I have not mentioned – but the blind faith that technology is actually being wisely harnessed and directed to the wellbeing of all is yesterday’s ‘tomorrow’s world’!</p> 
<p>The intent capacity to manipulate and control systems via the coercive imposition and intrusion upon them as an external agent is a particular kind of consciousness with a particular kind or result.</p> 
<p>What you may see is every kind of profitable manipulation intensified with regard to promoting the false sense of ‘freedom and security’ to live the life your are conditioned to accept and then become dependent on interventions of proprietary tech to manage and survive at all such a life.</p> 
<p>IE: interfere to make sleep chemically unnecessary by fooling the system to act as if it was etc – and then have a whole new raft of disease to ‘treat’ as a result of ******* everything up.</p> 
<p>What I see with the same information that you see is the obvious value of sleep as a part of valuing and awakening to the true nature of conscious existence. Here is wealth beyond your dreams! – and indeed including your dreams.</p>

